dct_description_sm: Drawn and Engraved for the Directory & Chronicle ; John Bartholomew & Co., Edinr.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Reference list of locations, with information on total area of lots and gardens and nurseries.
Shows roads (with Russian road names), railways, various locations, future harbour extension.
Map removed from "Directory & Chronicle" of unknown year.
